    <header>
      <div>
                  <a href="/users/hornet92/comments" title="View Hornet92 profile.">Hornet92</a>                          <time>Dec 28th 2011 7:01 GMT</time>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div><p>I think the private sector is the future of spaceflight.  It has happened in the past.  In the U.S., the military and the Postal Service developed many of the techniques to make long distance air travel practical, which was quickly put to use by the early airlines.  Even with the coming economic recovery, I don't think there is the political will to do much more in space at the moment.</p>
</div>
